Model Railroader - January 2014  USA

108 Pages | True PDF | English | 30 MB 


Model Railroader magazine publishes the information you need to build your own railroad. Each issue features step-by-step how-to projects; great model train layouts; and realistic track plans. You'll also get reviews of the latest locomotives, rolling stock, and accessories in HO, N, O, and other scales, expert tips, and more!
